Charles Stevenson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Stevenson_(actor) 0 Charles Stevenson (October 13, 1887 – July 4, 1943) was an American film actor of the silent era. He appeared in 136 films between 1914 and 1925. He was born in Sacramento, California, and died in Palo Alto, California.
